::Demolition::

He frowns at Zardus' reply. He just sits on the hatch.

::Dollon::

With all the chaos Dollon made his way to the temporary control
center.(Killfest's room.) He saw DrillBit.
"Commander. What are my orders?"

::DrillBit::

"Dollon, your with me. We're just waiting for StarScream."
